The basic law on '''[[copyright]] in [[Burundi]]''' is  ''Law No. 1/021 of December 30, 2005, on the Protection of Copyright and Related Rights in Burundi''.<ref>[http://www.wipo.int/wipolex/en/details.jsp?id=8323 ''Law No. 1/021 of December 30, 2005, on the Protection of Copyright and Related Rights in Burundi''.] [[WIPO]], 2013. Retrieved 24 December 2013.</ref> Burundi has not signed the [[Berne Convention]] but it has signed the [[TRIPS Agreement]].

